metadata.name: The Classical
metadata.description:
Description: A changing era in classical music was introduced during the times when the violin came into existence melting the soul from within and consuming the mind with it's beautiful intrinsic melody.

In this multi-colored painting, there are three Violinist in an emotional musical expression, painting a symbol of the in-depth of classical music. music and nature blending with each other expressed with the sunflowers, butterflies and the various grass and animals around.
